#: apps/core/templates/core/home.html:199
msgid ""
"Turning raw data into insight, from exploratory analysis and statistical "
"modelling to production-grade pipelines."
msgstr ""
"Rohdaten in Erkenntnisse verwandeln, von explorativer Analyse und statistischer Modellierung "
"bis hin zu produktionsreifen Pipelines."

#: apps/core/templates/core/home.html:223
msgid "Machine Learning & AI"
